<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien apat in ka vakvai,
 Tun In ka hun zuon;
 Gitlohna lam saupi ka hawh,
 Lalpa, In ka zuon.

[V2]
 In ka zuon, In ka zuon,
 Vakmang ta lo di'n;
 Lungsiet vang Nanga hing ka,
 Lalpa, In ka zuon.

[V3]
 2. Kum pha tmtak mawkin ka mang,
 Tun In ka hun zuon;
 Kisik in ka mitthi pumin,
 Lalpa, In ka zuon.

[V4]
 3. Gitloh suoka um ka khawptai,
 Tun In ka hun zuon;
 Ka ging, ka muong Na hehpihna,
 Lalpa, In ka zuon.

[V5]
 4. Ka thagau leh lunggil a chau,
 Tun In ka hun zuon;
 Hatna, kinepna a hung thak,
 Lalpa, In ka zuon.</lyrics>
<title>LORD, I'M COMING HOME</title>
<hymn_number>279</hymn_number>
</song>